{"tid":1717373,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【緊急】搞法院注意事項","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T15:31:12.000Z","uid":99762,"like":35,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d8a6bfbb3465cdb75b8a76eb85373425610c12","tid":1717373,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:56:21.000Z","msg":"搞法院前，你要注意啲咩<br />\n<br />\n一，法院、法官吃軟不吃硬<br />\n<br />\n如果手足對佢哋強硬，反彈亦越強<br />\n長遠而言，對我哋、尤其是被捕手足是大不利<br />\n<br />\n對付法院，方法係越膠越好(認真)<br />\n<br />\n換而之，是和理非做嘢的時候<br />\n<br />\n摺紙、寫信、貼 memo <br />\n<br />\n同法律界盡訴心中情<br />\n令佢哋共情我哋<br />\n<br />\n並且，假如之後法院的裁決仍然偏向政府的話<br />\n<br />\n手足放下魔法，是名正言順的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二，切勿用火魔<br />\n你可以用土、水、屎、蟲魔法<br />\n就是唔好用火魔<br />\n<br />\n你問點解？<br />\n因為香港人盲信法治<br />\n只要係「法治」，香港人就會信<br />\n即使入面已腐爛不堪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議，<br />\n如果要裝修，就用屎魔<br />\n<br />\n但是我認為<br />\n用和理非嗰套對抗法院，會係事半功倍"},{"pid":"eb91c86e4d9c07dcd5ec8f7fb3b0f85dbbc696e4","tid":1717373,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0096a904e85d2018a91ac615c51b402930f0d496","tid":1717373,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6c71ea404861ab24359db1659d342b5276a1fb8f","tid":1717373,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e84b10ddcb2d2b93ac55226856e70c9515fbd7c4","tid":1717373,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"最緊要係唔好傷人"},{"pid":"73cf050962096f5275b5a52061ff37801dbab9e7","tid":1717373,"uid":99762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8f31861f1d76fcaf0994b0bc17d70fe870d6aab4","tid":1717373,"uid":99762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e84b10ddcb2d2b93ac55226856e70c9515fbd7c4","tid":1717373,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score